title: powers conferred on me by section 3 of the European Communities Act 1972
heading: 3. Section 10 of the Act of 2014 is amended in subsection (2) by the
text_raw:
3. Section 10 of the Act of 2014 is amended in subsection (2) by the 

insertion of the following paragraph after paragraph (i): 

“(ia) to be, and to carry out the tasks of, the national rapporteur referred 
to in Article 19 of Directive 2011/36/EU of the European Parliament and 
of the Council of 5 April 20112 on preventing and combating trafficking 
in human beings and protecting its victims, and replacing Council 
Framework Decision 2002/629/JHA;”. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

5 October, 2020. 

HELEN MCENTEE, 

Minister for Justice and Equality. 

1 OJ No. L 101/1, 15.4.2011 
2 OJ No. L 101/1, 15.4.2011 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 16th October, 2020.
